parameters: ??? "I am here..."
Yui "Could it be, from this doll...?"
??? "Press the button on the chest."
Yui "The button on the chest...? Is it this one...?"
Yui "Ahhh!! The doll is!!"
??? "Hehe, it seems you can hear my heart's voice."

??? "To encounter someone with the qualifications so quickly, I'm
quite lucky."
Yui "Wh-What's this... Why is the doll...?"
Polka "Sorry for surprising you. I'm Polka. You're Yui-chan, right?"
Yui "Yes, that's right. But how do you know my name?"
Yui "And why can I... have a conversation with a doll?"

Polka "Hehe, I may look like a doll, but I was once a proper human
being."
Polka "Due to certain circumstances, I ended up in this form."
Yui "What is this... Am I seeing hallucinations..."

Yui "I've been studying so much lately I thought I was going crazy,
and now I've finally lost it... Ahh, do I need to be hospitalized...?"

Polka "...Your mind is perfectly normal. There's no need for
hospitalization."

Polka "Rather, the fact that you can hear my heart's voice means
there's no time for hospitalization."

Polka "Because from now on, you will become the warrior of light,
Pony-Celes, and fight against Zaidarg-G."

Yui "Pony-Celes, Zaidarg-G... I'm hearing strange words. Ahh... what
should I do. If this is a bad dream, please let me wake up..."
Polka "It can't be helped..."

Polka "Pull yourself together, Yui-chan. If you don't, your mother and
father, your friends, they all might be killed by Zaidarg-G."
Yui "...!? What do you mean!?"
Polka "You're finally willing to listen properly."
Yui "What do you mean by that!? Killed by Zaidarg-G? Explain properly!"

Polka (She's especially sensitive to people's misfortunes... Indeed,
you are the chosen warrior.)

Polka "What I'm about to tell you might be hard to believe, but it's
the truth. And I trust you enough to tell it."
Polka "So please trust me as well and listen."
Yui "...Alright."

Polka "Zaidarg-G is the name of a secret organization that seeks to
dominate this world."
Yui "...A secret organization called Zaidarg-G?"

Polka "Yes, an organization with thousands of combatants under the
absolute ruler named Darga-Noa."
Polka "And the organization that I destroyed... that was Zaidarg-G."
Yui "...Destroyed? Then..."
Polka "It's a story from hundreds of years ago."

Polka "Hundreds of years ago, I cornered Darga-Noa and destroyed
Zaidarg-G... At that time, I sealed Darga-Noa at the cost of my own
life."

Polka "However... time has passed, and somehow I have been revived in
this form in the modern era."

Polka "And although it's faint, I can feel it... that ominous dark
power in this modern era... the power of Darga-Noa."
Polka "Just like me, he has been resurrected in this modern era..."
Yui "...Such a thing. Then what should we do?"

Polka "Having used all my power to seal Darga-Noa, I am now
regrettably nothing more than a doll..."
Polka "I've even become unable to transform into Pony-Celes..."
Yui "...Pony-Celes?"

Polka "The warrior of light... no, the warrior who banishes darkness
with the sacred light, that's the Holy Flash Princess Pony-Celes."
Yui "...Holy Flash Princess Pony-Celes."
Polka "And now, I have a request for you."

Polka "I want you to protect this world from Zaidarg-G as Pony-Celes.
You have the qualifications for it."
Yui "Me, as Pony-Celes...?"

Yui "Th-that's impossible! Thousands of combatants... and Darga-Noa
with the power of darkness!? I'm just a normal student."

Polka "No, you can do it. If you can hear the voice of your heart,
then you can."

Yui "Even if you say that... I mean, I'm somewhat confident in karate.
But there's no way I can fight against an evil emperor like in an
anime."
Polka "Then let's try it. With this Holy Brooch."
Yui "Holy Brooch?"

Polka "If you are qualified, this brooch will recognize you and grant
you the power of Pony-Celes."

Polka "If not, then you will forget everything we talked about today
and return to your normal life."
Polka "What do you say?"

Yui "Well, if it's just trying... there's no way I have such
qualifications."
Polka "It's decided then!"

Polka "Place this brooch on your chest and shout 'Pony-Celes, Holy
Up'."
Yui "Eh... shout... it's embarrassing..."
Polka "Just do as I say!"
Yui "If I must do it..."
Yui "Pony-Celes, Holy Up..."
Polka "Say it louder!!!"
Yui "Alright, I got it!"
Yui "Pony-Celes, Holy Up!!!"

Yui's mother "Yui!! Don't suddenly shout like that; you're bothering
the neighbors!!"
Yui's mother "Dinner is ready, so come quickly!!"
Pony-Celes "Hey! Because I shouted, mom got mad at me!"
Polka "More importantly, look at yourself."
Pony-Celes "What is this outfit!!"
Pony-Celes "And this hair color!"

Pony-Celes "No... more than that, this power overflowing from my
entire body. What is this..."
Polka "That power is Holy Energy. The light that vanquishes darkness."
Polka "It's decided. Indeed, you are the chosen warrior."

Pony-Celes "With this power, I feel like I can win against any
opponent. Amazing, Polka..."
Polka "Yui-chan, I ask you once again."

Polka "Please protect the town from Zaidarg-G as Pony-Celes in my
stead."
Polka "Even if it's just until my power returns... please, I beg you."
Pony-Celes "Polka..."
Pony-Celes "..."
Pony-Celes "Geez, can't be helped..."

Pony-Celes "I'll do it until Polka's power returns! Until then... I'll
somehow protect the town!"
Polka "Yui-chan... thank you..."

Pony-Celes "Honestly, I'm still a bit skeptical, but Polka doesn't
seem like a bad person... Besides, I can't stand by and let people
suffer. That would make me the bad guy."
Polka "I'm counting on you from now on, Yui-chan!"
Pony-Celes "Yeah, let's do our best, Polka!"

Polka "Ah, I forgot to mention, but you can't let anyone know that
you're Pony-Celes."

Polka "If rumors spread and the Zaidarg-G guys identify you, we'll be
finished before we can destroy Zaidarg-G."
Pony-Celes "Understood..."

Polka "Ah, and... now that I've calmed down, I'm really hungry, so
please prepare some food!"
Polka "Even in this form, I make sure to eat three meals a day."

Polka "Ah, and if there's dessert after the meal, that would make me
happy."

Polka "Of course, my presence here is a secret from your family.
Things might get a bit tough starting today, but hang in there!"
Pony-Celes "..."
Pony-Celes "What are you saying as if it's someone else's problem!"

Pony-Celes "You're not mistaking me for some kind of servant, are
you?!"

Pony-Celes "I'm already busy with my studies, and now I have to fight
evil as Pony-Celes and take care of your meals too?!"
Pony-Celes "Hah... impossible, there's no way I can do all that!"
Polka "If it's Yui-chan, you can do it!"
Polka "You can do it if you try!!"
Pony-Celes "Don't talk like Timon and Pumbaa!!"

Polka "Becoming Pony-Celes seems to have boosted your retort skills
too. Fufufu."
Pony-Celes "..."

Yui's Mother "Yui!! I told you to come quickly! If you don't come now,
I'm clearing away the meal!"
Pony-Celes "No way~~!! Wait for me~~! I'm so hungry~~!!"
Polka "Ah, that outfit is a problem..."

Yui's Mother "What are you wearing?! And what's with that hair
color?!!"
Pony-Celes "...Ah."
Pony-Celes "...This is, well... cosplay or something..."

Yui's Mother "What cosplay?! Changing your hair to look like a
delinquent! As punishment, no dinner for you tonight!"
Pony-Celes "...I don't want that----!!!"
